name: Hackerspace 4933 empty demo
description:
This is a representational model for THS's new  4933 space,   with no shops installed.  It is intended to give THS members and idea of what 4933 looks like, or can look like, with out requiring them to visit during coronavirus.

If there is particular interest, I may add features or demo spaces.

CLICK 'Run Game" TO PLAY!

WASD to move, mouse to steer and look around.  space jumps
